{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XDjxyLwkaMXpxX2UKGshtf","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Story 15-3 is complete. Here is a summary:\n\n**Implementation already done by a previous session** — verified and marked for review.\n\n### What was implemented:\n\n1. **`src/lib/templates.ts`** — `renderTemplate()` (string interpolation) and `renderTemplateFile()` (file read + interpolation) functions added\n2. **Static template files created:**\n   - `templates/dockerfiles/` — Dockerfile.nodejs, Dockerfile.python, Dockerfile.rust, Dockerfile.generic, Dockerfile.multi-stage.tmpl\n   - `templates/compose/` — victoria.yml, collector-only.yml, otel-collector-base.yaml, otel-collector-remote.yaml\n   - `templates/docs/` — readme.md.tmpl\n   - `templates/prompts/` — ralph-prompt.md\n   - `templates/otlp/` — nodejs.md, python.md, rust.md\n3. **TypeScript generators migrated to `renderTemplateFile()` calls:**\n   - `src/templates/docker-compose.ts`\n   - `src/templates/otel-config.ts`\n   - `src/templates/readme.ts`\n   - `src/lib/agents/ralph-prompt.ts`\n   - `src/modules/infra/dockerfile-template.ts`\n   - `src/lib/stacks/nodejs.ts`, `python.ts`, `rust.ts`\n4. **Test file** — `src/templates/__tests__/template-migration.test.ts` with 31 tests covering all ACs\n\n### Test results:\n- template-migration.test.ts: 31/31 passed\n- showboat-template.test.ts: 17/17 passed\n- dockerfile-template.test.ts: 56/56 passed\n- init-project.test.ts + index.test.ts: 32/32 passed\n\nStory status set to `review` with all 3 ACs checked.\n\n## Session Issues\n\n- `verify-prompt.ts` and `showboat-template.ts` were not migrated to static templates because they contain complex programmatic logic (conditionals, loops, switch statements) that cannot be expressed as simple `{{VAR}}` interpolation. This is consistent with the story's note about `bmad-patches.ts` (\"evaluate if this is truly a template or code generation\"). These files are correc