ateFile('templates/prompts/ralph-prompt.md', {...})`\n- `src/modules/infra/dockerfile-template.ts` — uses `renderTemplateFile()` for Dockerfile generation\n- `src/lib/stacks/nodejs.ts`, `python.ts`, `rust.ts` — stack providers use `renderTemplateFile()` for Dockerfile sections\n\nFiles NOT migrated (intentionally — complex programmatic logic):\n- `src/templates/verify-prompt.ts` — contains conditionals, loops, switch statements\n- `src/templates/showboat-template.ts` — contains complex logic\n\n---\n\n## AC 3: renderTemplate() returns identical output to former TypeScript functions\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:**\n\n31 dedicated tests in `src/templates/__tests__/template-migration.test.ts` verify output equivalence:\n- `renderTemplate()` core function: 4 tests (substitution, unmatched vars, multiple occurrences, empty vars)\n- `renderTemplateFile()` file loading: 3 tests (basic, with vars, missing file throws)\n- AC1 directory structure: 5 tests (dockerfiles, compose, prompts, docs, otlp dirs exist with expected files)\n- AC3 output equivalence: 12 tests (each template file produces expected content with correct placeholders)\n- AC2 generator replacement: 7 tests (each migrated TS file calls renderTemplateFile and returns valid content)\n\nAll 31 tests pass. Full test suite: 3777 tests pass, 97.1% coverage.\n\n```\nTest Files  145 passed (145)\n     Tests  3777 passed (3777)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| AC | Verdict | Method |\n|----|---------|--------|\n| AC1 | PASS | File system inspection + tests |\n| AC2 | PASS | Source code grep + tests |\n| AC3 | PASS | 31 equivalence tests |\n\n**Overall: PASS** — all 3 ACs verified with direct evidence.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":181,"cache_read_input_tokens":65786,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":181},"output_tokens":57,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_availab